The resources protected by UMA must be registered in oxTrust. The following propterties describe a resource:   name  scopes  type  icon_uri   The resource type can be a string, URI or any other supported value type supported by Gluu Server CE. The properties shown above are not concrete, and it is possible that a resource may contain custom properties. An example of the resource JSON is given beow:  {
"name":"scim_access",
"icon_uri":"https:\/\/centos.gluu.info\/identity\/uma\/scope\/file\/scim_access"
